Package: CuspCatastrophe
Type: Package
Title: Cusp Catastrophe (Shiny) Interactive Topological and Dynamical Systems Tool
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: person("Michael", "Geuss", email = "mgeuss@bowiestate.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A Shiny app for exploring cusp catastrophe topology (potential function and equilibria)
    and a separate statistical instantiation layer via a 2D change-equation phase space (vector field).
